questions.question: Would you rather always be 10 minutes late or always be 20 minutes early?
Would you rather lose all of your money and valuables or all of the pictures you have ever taken?
questions.firstAnswer: lose all of your money and valuables
questions.secondAnswer: all of the pictures you have ever taken

questions.question: Would you rather be able to see 10 minutes into your own future or 10 minutes into the future of anyone but yourself?
questions.firstAnswer: be able to see 10 minutes into your own future
questions.secondAnswer: 10 minutes into the future of anyone but yourself

questions.question: Would you rather be famous when you are alive and forgotten when you die or unknown when you are alive but famous after you die?
questions.firstAnswer: be famous when you are alive and forgotten when you die
questions.secondAnswer: unknown when you are alive but famous after you die

questions.question: Would you rather go to jail for 4 years for something you didn’t do or get away with something horrible you did but always live in fear of being caught?
questions.firstAnswer: go to jail for 4 years for something you didn’t do
questions.secondAnswer: get away with something horrible you did but always live in fear of being caught
